Package: geosmooth
Title: Geometric Smoothing and Conditional Expectation Methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Pawel",
           family = "Gajer",
           email = "pgajer@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Pawel Gajer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Pawel Gajer <pgajer@gmail.com>
Description: Provides geometric smoothing and conditional expectation
    estimation methods split from the gflow package. The initial development
    focus is local polynomial smoothing, model-averaged local polynomial
    smoothing, local polynomial lifting trend filtering, synchronized local
    polynomial lifting trend filtering, and SSRHE.
